<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Brasilia June 20 <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/9098988@N02/9098629686/in/photolist-eS1RBC-eRPpE2-71NY6A-71K1rD-71K2dz-71P3Ls-71NXKN-71NZGh-71NXzU-71K2DR-71K31k-71K3pK-71P1Sb-71JWSV-71JXmD-71K186-71JZcF-71NXDC-71NYQW-71P4xL-71JYsH-eS1Shs-eRPqPt-eRPqHX-eS1Smb-eS1Ss3-eS1SiU-eRFnjL-eRF25E-eRu5za-eRFGwu-eRtzMB-eRFAX5-eRF7EU-eRumNa-eRtKE4-eRu81e-eRug3T-71P49y-eRuaK6-eRupEM-eRFpXE-eRtFwx-dZuMYQ-eQdKR4-eQdKCp-eQq7Ym-eQdLp8-eQdL2D-2TGgP-bCnYy">Semilla Luz)</a></strong></p>
